metadata.name: Waiting
metadata.description:
Is it Tuesday? 
When will it be Tuesday? 
I’m permitted happiness on Tuesday. 
I’ll extinguish my soul until the hour hand strikes that lovely 24-hour cove of time one day después Monday! 
When will it be Tuesday?
Is it Tuesday?

Collaborative Jolt Of Expression (CJOE) are unique 1/1 versions of a GJOE as imagined by Custom Horror.

I’m beyond humbled to be included in this collection, sharing space with world-class artists.

‘Waiting’ is a digital art created via collage and sketch work and Photoshop editing. The frenetic, graffiti tag-influenced motif asks the viewer about their present day life. More importantly, for both the viewer and looking glass creator, the idiosyncratic canvas urges — don’t wait to chase after your dream life.
 
Tuesday isn’t coming.

Make it happen.

One.
